{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/Oppidum_Logo.png?t=1738662023\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The fate of a marvelous world depends on you. Will you live up to the challenge?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the land of Insule, discover every resource it has to offer and collect it to craft your equipment in classic survival-crafting fashion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/EN_01_StorydrivenSurvival.png?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/2024_11_Store_Gif_01.gif?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Everything you do in Oppidum will help you achieve your ultimate goal</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You've been summoned to the island of Insule as its last hope. Every battle you fight, every item you craft and every inhabitant you help will put you closer to that goal: saving this magical world from its corrupted fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/EN_02_BringInsuleTogether.png?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/2024_11_Store_Gif_02.gif?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Link neighbors to each other and restore a divided land to their former bonds</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The corruption crawled its way into a divided society. Meet a diverse cast of characters, assist them and let them teach you about the ways of Insule. By earning their trust, you will also help them regain their own trust in each other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/EN_03_BuildASafeHaven.png?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/2024_11_Store_Gif_03.gif?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Your camp is your refuge and base of operations; craft, rest and get ready for the next adventure.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everything begins and ends at your camp, where you will craft equipment, construct buildings, tend to your crops and animals or cook energizing meals. Earn new blueprints for useful structures, or simply decorate it to make it feel like home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/EN_04_FaceGrowingChallenges.png?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/2024_11_Store_Gif_04.gif?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Don't let your guard down on an island driven mad by the corruption.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you push through Insule, the corrupted island will show its fangs back at you. Arm yourself with weapons and armors to emerge victorious of every challenge. Hunt for resources, defend yourself and seek the guidance of the Protectors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/EN_05_HarnessTheTamai.png?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/2024_11_Store_Gif_05.gif?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gather and take advantage of Tamai, the root of all things on Insule</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everything in Insule is sustained by Tamai, an energy unique to the land, the same that has brought you to it. You will feel its presence all around, and it will prove essential once you learn how to gather it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/EN_06_CollaborativeAdventure.png?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/extras/2024_11_Store_Gif_06.gif?t=1738662023\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The weight of a prophecy lies on your shoulders, but you don't have to carry it alone. Enjoy Oppidum as a solo adventure, or with up to 3 other players.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your friends will be summoned to Insule along with you. Turn this tale into a cooperative adventure to save the land. Venture into the woods, swamps and caves with your friends, collaborate to build your camp and complete quests together. </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738662023","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/page.bg.jpg?t=1738662023","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/0ca5dde83b523fb473a99b01ddab5b5029df7880/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738662023","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115760/0ca5dde83b523fb473a99b01ddab5b5029df7880/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738662023","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9